reviewText:
Many things are broken in this game:
- No matter the graphics settings, it runs at max. 25-30 fps. Using flamers make it even worst (with i7 @ 3.4Ghz, HD radeon 7900 series, latest drivers);
- Couple of spelling mistakes here and there in the text - feels like the game has been rushed to release on time;
- The sales speech talks about 3 chapters available when you actually have only 1 option: ultramarines. Blood Angles have nothing specific (boring) and don't even try to play Space Wolves, you would just get smashed on hand to hand combat (where they are supposed to excel...) and will spend countless hours reloading your game (even more boring);
- A few bugs: overwatch fire not working when supposed to, terminator not seeing" the stealers when they are just in front of them
